<li id="cite_note-Einstein1909-31">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Einstein1909_31-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Einstein1909_31-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Einstein1909_31-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFEinstein1909"><a href="/wiki/Albert_Einstein" title="Albert Einstein">Einstein, A.</a> (1909). "Über die Entwicklung unserer Anschauungen über das Wesen und die Konstitution der Strahlung". <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Physikalische_Zeitschrift&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Physikalische Zeitschrift (page does not exist)">Physikalische Zeitschrift</a></i> <b>10</b>: 817–825.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=%C3%9Cber+die+Entwicklung+unserer+Anschauungen+%C3%BCber+das+Wesen+und+die+Konstitution+der+Strahlung&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BPhysikalische+Zeitschrift%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Einstein&amp;rft.aufirst=A.&amp;rft.au=Einstein%2C+A.&amp;rft.date=1909&amp;rft.volume=10&amp;rft.pages=817%E2%80%93825&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Photon"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(German)</span>. An <a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Development_of_Our_Views_on_the_Composition_and_Essence_of_Radiation" class="extiw" title="s:The Development of Our Views on the Composition and Essence of Radiation">English translation</a> is available from <a href="/wiki/Wikisource" title="Wikisource">Wikisource</a>.</li>
